snippet.textDisplay: I uploaded a track from Halo 4, so I figured I'd upload one from the other big shooter coming out. My experience with this series is next to none: I finished the first Call of Duty and played a couple Modern Warfare multiplayer matches at a friend's house. The soundtrack is mostly composed by Jack Wall but this particular track isn't. It's completely different from the rest since it (probably) plays around a night club. It's a really solid track actually.
